file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3

info:
  title: Ping API
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /ping:
    post:
      operationId: pingBody
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                ping:
                  type: string
              required:
                - ping
      responses:
        200:
          description: Returns value of ping
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  pong:
                    type: string

  /ping/{value}:
    parameters:
      - name: value
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      operationId: ping
      responses:
        200:
          description: Returns value
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  pong:
                    type: string
